node.text:
just a quick #earSwap  at #animalkingdomLodge ((my favorite!!)) 🦁🌴🦁🌴 It's amazing how much I feel at home at AK Lodge
I remember staying as a kid and just begging to be allowed to meander through the lobby and out to see the animals. I loved the smell, the firepits, the storytellers even the big lion on the wall in the gift shop just feels like home to me. And of course as you pull in there's the welcome home sign on the guard shack. 
I just love it 💚 .
.
✨Jambo means home to me ✨ ✨✨✨✨✨✨✨✨✨✨
.
.
.
.

node.text:
💚 mama 💚

It's still a little weird to me that I'm someones mama! 
Becoming a mom wasn't high on my priority list. I didn't have the easiest journey with the women in my life so when it came time to join the ranks of motherhood I wasn't excited or ready.
.
.
What if I messed up? What if I didn't like it, or worse what if babe didn't like me? 
I had the best time this morning hanging out with lots of other moms and it's just a gift to hear that they all have fears, struggles, and insecurities too! We are just figuring it out and the best thing we can do is give each other and ourselves G✨R✨A✨C✨E .
.
Now I love being a Mama and it's a badge of honor to wear my Mama ear in my happiest most magical place with my sweet babe!! ✨✨✨✨✨✨✨✨✨✨
.
.
.
.

node.text:
A FAMILY AFFAIR 💚✨💚✨💚
.
.
Like so many out there Disney for me has always been a place for family.  It never mattered what was happening, good or bad. When our family was at #waltDisneyWorld everything was great.
.
.
Today I got to send an order out to two of the ladies who taught me all about Disney! They are legit park warriors who open and close the parks like it's nothing. Beyond that they spend so much time making sure every detail is thought through for our family to have the best time possible. .
.
It's an honor to share our magic with them and I can't wait to see them rocking their custom ears!! ✨✨✨✨✨✨✨✨✨✨
.
.
.
.
